Karadin Said:<br>
&quot;I’ve also seen you post about how, because they won’t see the higher end of PoP they might as well quit EQ. I ask then, should everyone who hasn’t been to N ToV also quit? Or Emperor? Or Vex Thal? These are all high end content that most of the Rathe guilds will never see, and cannot team up to go to. Why do you figure PoP should be any different? Just because United Necros will never see Vex Thal or Plane of Time is not a reason to quit EQ.&quot;<br>
<br>
Actually what I said was:<br>
&quot;I feel sorry for anyone who is not in a guild capable of taking down the flag mobs if the teaming is deemed to be &quot;unfair&quot; since they might as well quit playing if they want to see any of the upper end PoP content. <br>
