And your trying to use a moral loophole to manipulate the rules in the &quot;spirit of the RTA&quot; <br>
<br>
<br>
Karadin Said:<br>
&quot;I’m sorry you have a misguided idea of what the RTA was created for, but it was not so that United Necros has an equal shot at Plane of Time/VT/ST/VP. It was setup so that all guilds/alliances that can actually kill any particular raid-level content can do so with as few headaches as possible&quot;<br>
<br>
Translation:<br>
The RTA was designed to keep the smaller guilds &quot;headaches&quot; out of your zones??? It was NOT designed for everyone to have an equal shot? <br>
<br>
<br>
Karadin Said:<br>
&quot;In order to be an alliance for one mob on rotation you have to be an alliance for ALL rotations, not just the ones you pick and choose&quot;<br>
