Does the RTA have the right to enforce its moral opinions and rotation mob rules on non rotation mobs?<br>
<br>
Karadin Said:<br>
&quot;However, what you cannot disregard is that the RTA is a *player-made* system on the Rathe that goes beyond SOE’s rules, and thus IS about enforcing group views. So when someone says “Hey, its not against the rules from SOE”, even if they’re right, its irrelevant&quot; <br>
<br>
