People also keep mentioning that theres nothing stopping guilds teaming up to take other mobs out as well.  Well to be blunt, if you think that get your head examined.  It's comparing apples to oranges, if you think a co-op effort on a PoP mob is similar in ANY WAY to a co-op effort on AoW/Emp/whoever.<br>
<br>
