<br>
But what if 50 people are allready flagged?  22 more to get flagged, which means 50 flags would still be left over.  Not hard to take those 50 people out of the raid, is it.  And that WILL happen.  Maybe not on Rathe, but on other servers it most likely has allready.<br>
<br>
And would anyone begrudge a guild as large as Tindi or BotS from beringing flagged people to a raid to ensure the rest get flagged?  Next thing you know the RTA will start making rules you can only have a max of 72 people along.<br>
